  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Boris Johnson is ready for the NATO job",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior members of the Conservative Party are backing outgoing British Prime Minister Boris Johnson's bid to become the next NATO secretary-general, The Telegraph reports.",
        "Jens Stoltenberg, the current head of the US-led military alliance, is expected to resign in September next year, the newspaper said.",
        "It suggests that this period will give Johnson some time to recharge his batteries after a three-year run as British Prime Minister.",
        "The 58-year-old announced his resignation earlier this month after a high-profile scandal among his cabinet ministers forced him to resign."
      ],
